{"timestamp":"  55.851280170s","level":"DEBUG","fields":{"message":"Adding tool results to context","results":"[ToolResult { name: ToolName(\"todo_write\"), call_id: Some(ToolCallId(\"call_00_UpNZSY9dN56bYJLuDw57S6rf\")), output: ToolOutput { is_error: false, values: [Text(\"<todos_updated\\n  changes=\\\"13\\\"\\n>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 1: INBOX-CHECK - Check refinery mail and clean up wisps\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 2: QUEUE-SCAN - Scan merge queue for pending branches\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 3: PROCESS-BRANCH - Mechanical rebase of polecat branch\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 4: RUN-TESTS - Quality checks and test suite\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 5: QUALITY-REVIEW - Review merge diff\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 6: HANDLE-FAILURES - Verification gate\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 7: MERGE-PUSH - Merge and push to target\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 8: LOOP-CHECK - Check for more branches\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 9: GENERATE-SUMMARY - Summarize patrol cycle\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 10: CHECK-INTEGRATION-BRANCHES - Integration branch readiness\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 11: CONTEXT-CHECK - Session health assessment\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 12: PATROL-CLEANUP - End-of-cycle inbox hygiene\\n</todo>\\n<todo\\n  status=\\\"pending\\\"\\n  change=\\\"added\\\"\\n>Step 13: BURN-OR-LOOP - Loop or handoff decision\\n</todo>\\n</todos_updated>\")] } }]"},"filename":"crates/forge_domain/src/context.rs","line_number":515}
